Package org.bukkit.entity.minecart

Interfaces for various Minecart types.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CommandMinecart  
ExplosiveMinecart Represents a Minecart with TNT inside it that can explode when triggered.
HopperMinecart Represents a Minecart with a Hopper inside it
PoweredMinecart Represents a powered minecart.
RideableMinecart Represents a minecart that can have certain entities as passengers.
SpawnerMinecart Represents a Minecart with an entity spawner inside it.
StorageMinecart Represents a minecart with a chest.
